    Gene markers of 29 immune cell types

    ABIS_markers.Rd

    List of immune markers from Monaco et al.

    ABIS_markers

    Format

    dataframe

    Source

    ABIS

    References

    Monaco et al. (2019) Cell reports vol. 26,6 (PubMed)

    Examples

    data(ABIS_markers)
head(ABIS_markers)
